title: Gardner-Webb Drops Series Opener Friday At No. 7 Georgia Tech - Gardner Webb University Bulldogs
content: Gardner-Webb Drops Series Opener Friday At No. 7 Georgia Tech  Gardner Webb University Bulldogs
description: ATLANTA – Gardner-Webb faced its second top-10 opponent of the season on Friday afternoon, falling at 7th-ranked Georgia Tech, 14-0, in its first road game of 2022.
